text: This obsoletes IRM 4.26.2, Bank Secrecy Act, Program Structure.

The material relating to Bank Secrecy Act Program Structure previously contained in IRM 4.26.2 is incorporated into revised IRM 4.26.1 , Introduction and Program Structure. The information contained in this IRM was moved to provided a more concise overview of the Bank Secrecy Act Program in SB/SE in a single IRM.
